## IGenericIdentifierType type

Represents a generic type name (i.e. <T> or <S>)

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type IGenericIdentifierType<T extends string = string> = {
    type: 'generic_identifier';
    definition: T;
};
```
